high_descs: Go through this room and head the pathway on the left, then take a right into the hallway, heading straight to the room with a bed ahead, then approach the dresser to the right of the bed.
Pick up the butterknife from the bed.
Exit the room the way you came in and walk down the hallway again, turning left into the room you started, then head to the bread on the wall to the right.
Slice the bread on the shelf beneath the TV.
Place the butterknife down on the tvstand.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn right and head through the room to the white fridge near the corner to the right.
Put the bread in the fridge, let it cool, then remove it.
Head to the microwave to the left of the fridge.
Place the bread in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Slice a loaf of Bread, cool one slice in a fridge, and place that slice in a Microwave.
